# SAFE SHORT .gitignore (~50 patterns)
# Intended use: paste this into your existing .gitignore (or replace if you want a minimal baseline).
# Focus: avoid over-aggressive media ignores; include only common junk + build/caches + leak prevention.

############################
# 1) OS / editor / misc junk
############################
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
Desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db?
Icon
Icon?
.Trash-*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.Fseventsd
.Spotlight-V100
.TemporaryItems
.VolumeIcon.icns

*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*~
*.bak
*.tmp
*.log
*.pid
*.seed
*.dmp
core
core.*

############################
# 2) Build artifacts
############################
dist/
build/
out/
public/build/
.cache/
.vite/
.next/
.nuxt/
.svelte-kit/
.storybook/
storybook-static/

**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/

############################
# 3) Dependencies / caches
############################
node_modules/
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage/

# Virtual envs
.venv/
venv/
ENV/

############################
# 4) Secrets / leak prevention (strong)
############################
# Environment files
.env
.env.*

# Generic secret filename patterns
secrets.*
secret.*
credentials.*
credential.*

# Key/cert patterns (private material)
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.cer
*.jks

# Token-ish filenames (reduce accidental commits)
*.jwt
*.token
*.tokens
*.refresh
access-token.*
refresh-token.*
api-keys.*
api_key.*

# NOTE: do NOT ignore your music/media content; this file avoids *.mp3/*.wav/*.png/etc.

############################
# 5) Logs / crash dumps / test reports
############################
*.trace
*.stacktrace
*.stackdump
*.crash

coverage/
nyc_output/
*.lcov
junit.xml
test-results/
